                <text>The definition of <emphasis style="bold">fines defaulter</emphasis> in section 85A(6) is amended by adding the following paragraph:</text>
                <amend increment="1" quote="1">
                  <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">f</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>any amount payable under section 138A(1) of the Sentencing Act 2002</text>
